{"tid":1418534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班狗向空氣推進同成日攪到好夜，其實係文宣","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T18:33:53.000Z","uid":204246,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50a63f666969f726c9f229eaf44e37fd8368895e","tid":1418534,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:05:00.000Z","msg":"班狗咁做係因為搏D受影響既居民唔會望同上網求証<br />\n聽到聲就會覺得手足重係度抗爭緊<br />\n第二朝CcTVB再輕輕講清場行動直到凌晨<br />\n咁個班輕藍輕黃又比狗嘈到無交好訓既<br />\n就自然怪班手足，唔好睇少呢點<br />\n積埋積埋會影響到民意<br />\n我地可以係文宣上盡可能解釋比人知<br />\n係班狗夜晚無晒人重擾民，唔係重有人抗爭<br />\n呢D陰招好易比人當笑柄，忽略左佢既威力<br />\n總之班狗越做ON9野，笑完之後越要諗一諗動機"},{"pid":"23cc22b045c5707c1d627311fb1efaae89cf1174","tid":1418534,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:10:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8231e306a0787425c580aade162136f47894b08","tid":1418534,"uid":260639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6771fcdc171b234880882487c1d491aa907acf","tid":1418534,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5330992606a52caa58844b301a8e85e988102af3","tid":1418534,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32ab46f4757cf34f30268cd535d4173bbe16932a","tid":1418534,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef2917799c2fa3051d13fc2b398aa86a060f101f","tid":1418534,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:13:15.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"b27395f5c381093d18f3543b520f611596f5a0af","tid":1418534,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:56:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e8fb6408f0d8f7c63d9f5e3cdc7a0adb6095068","tid":1418534,"